{"tid":1667890,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"泰國宮心計 王室撤銷王妃詩妮娜所有銜頭","createTime":"2019-10-21T16:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T15:46:15.000Z","uid":152123,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"caee7b90608d03f86231d3f88b7173eda98f00ec","tid":1667890,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"泰國王室撤銷王妃詩妮娜所有軍事和王室銜頭<br />\n<br />\n泰國王室宣佈，撤銷王妃詩妮娜所有的軍事和王室銜頭。詩妮娜於今年7月28日，獲泰王哇集拉隆功冊封為王妃，但王室認為，詩妮娜對泰王不夠忠誠，不滿足於自己的地位，試圖與王后平起平起，形容詩妮娜為沒有為泰王帶來榮譽，亦不了解王室傳統，所以撤銷她的王室及軍事銜頭。詩妮娜是一位合資格機師、前軍方護士和王室保鏢。<br />\n<br />\nRTHK 2019-10-22 00:29:25"},{"pid":"0eeafd18f94b5757b690480d4c51c799ac154aa7","tid":1667890,"uid":20170,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:55:16.000Z","msg":"泰王有得三妻四妾咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36a33d97f63eb2ce142de71bef8b6aba9889cb3","tid":1667890,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1487520_1_L_20191022002925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1487520_1_L_20191022002925.jpg&h=19225828&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77072ad178be9fa49909d6ecebc66f2e3daba067","tid":1667890,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media5.orientaldaily.com.my/storage/resize_cache/images/uploads/news-cover/2019/August_2019/20190827/098089089.jpg/3a89a76d985decfd7ce59bd4f56eed8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia5.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fstorage%2Fresize_cache%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2Fnews-cover%2F2019%2FAugust_2019%2F20190827%2F098089089.jpg%2F3a89a76d985decfd7ce59bd4f56eed8b.jpg&h=7bd43b52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c521930cc77cfdfa5219be3da8572098720947ba","tid":1667890,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T1