-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"0026cea73d1435288282ee25e840c9eb1a8c928e","tid":1667890,"uid":15605,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bbd51dbcfd1b2971246214fec4fc01128b198141","tid":1667890,"uid":49853,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"詩妮娜是一位合資格機師、前軍方護士和王室保鏢。<br />\n<br />\n最撚勁既王妃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:30:34.000Z","msg":"王后仲勁呀，由平民空姐到泰王保鏢隊長仲搶埋個王后做"},{"pid":"f87f2274e2c87ea7f2ab62fab230c07165fb1e90","tid":1667890,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"泰國王室同共匪有密切關係 睇路"},{"pid":"9c0c709d7c5696cffae7bea4b2c76d914025e6b3","tid":1667890,"uid":5303,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:32:56.000Z","msg":"嫁左幾個月就比人收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2e3fbfd2da5fc277becbd7f